cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper deals with text analysis and plagiarism detection, which are common topics in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and cryptography (cs.CR). However, since the study focuses on medical theses and articles, the most likely sub-category is cs.DL, which deals with digital libraries and information retrieval in specific domains. The other sub-categories are also relevant, but to a lesser extent.
